            Association</b>, <i>Career of Distinguished Scholarship Award 1997</i></li>
          <li><b>World History Association</b>, <i>First Book Prize 1999</i></li>
          <li><b>Political Economy of the World-System Section of the American Sociological
            Association</b>, <i>Book Award 2000 for ReORIENT</i> </li>
